Time / Dates Analysis

Break down Crm Cd Desc by

  • Area Name
  • Month of Year
  • Day of week

Area Plots

s1 <- LAcrime %>%
  group_by(area = `AREA NAME`,
           crime = `Crm Cd Desc`) %>%
  summarize(count = n()) %>%
  arrange(desc(count)) %>%
  filter(count > 1000)
 
s1 %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = crime, y = count, fill = crime)) +
  geom_bar(stat = 'identity') + 
  facet_wrap(~ area)

Month of Year

s2 <- LAcrime %>%
  group_by(month_rpt = rpted_month,
           crime = `Crm Cd Desc`) %>%
  summarize(count = n()) %>%
  arrange(desc(count)) %>%
  filter(count > 1000)

s2 %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = crime, y = count, fill = crime)) +
  geom_bar(stat = 'identity') +
  facet_wrap(~month_rpt)
